Lending-related fees include fees earned from loan
commitments, standby letters of credit, financial
guarantees, and other loan-servicing activities. Deposit-
related fees include fees earned from providing
overdraft and other deposit account services, and from
performing cash management activities. Lending- and
deposit-related fees in this revenue category are
recognized over the period in which the related service
is provided.
