Net gains/(losses) on sales of loans and lending-related commitments (including adjustments to record loans and
lending-related commitments held-for-sale at the lower of cost or fair value) recognized in noninterest revenue was
$(43) million for the year ended December 31, 2020 of which $(36) million was related to loans. Net gains on sales of
