where the sole concession granted is the discharge of debt, loans with short-term or other insignificant modifications
that are not considered concessions, and loans for which the Firm has elected to apply the option to suspend the
application of accounting guidance for TDRs as provided by the CARES Act and extended by the Consolidated
Appropriations Act.
